#API Endpoints Summary
Method	Endpoint	Purpose
GET	/api/documents/certificates/	List all TC/Certificate applications (Filter by Status/Student).
POST	/api/documents/certificates/	Create a new application with attachments.
POST	/api/documents/certificates/{id}/approve/	Approve the application and update the timeline.
GET	/api/documents/certificates/{id}/preview_tc/	Generate data for the "Transfer Certificate Preview"